## Compliance

We comply with:

- California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA)
- General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) - for EU users
- Apple App Store Guidelines
- Children's Online Privacy Protection Act (COPPA)

## Third-Party Links

Our app may contain links to external websites or articles. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites.

## International Users

If you access our app from outside the United States, your information may be transferred to and processed in the United States. By using our app, you consent to this transfer.

